<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />Let them all praise the name of Yahweh,</para>

<para style="q1">for his name alone is exalted</para>

<para style="q1">and his glory extends over the earth and the heavens.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />He has lifted up the horn of his people</para>

<para style="q1">for praise from all his faithful ones,</para>

<para style="q1">the Israelites, the people near to him.</para>

<para style="q1">Praise Yahweh.</para>
